Subject: [PATCH 1/5] Phase 1: Add category toggles and progression
 restrictions to ModConfig

Entry 5 in Project_Development.md:

Added 9 new properties to ModConfig.cs:
- 8 category master toggles (all default to true for backward compatibility)
  - EnablePlayerAndTools
  - EnableFarmAndFishing
  - EnableRelationships
  - EnableSkills
  - EnableTime
  - EnableWarps
  - EnableWeather
  - EnableAdvanced

- 1 progression restriction toggle (defaults to false - unrestricted)
  - EnforceWarpProgressionRestrictions

Properties organized with clear section comments and XML documentation.
Backward compatible with existing config.json files.
No build errors - compilation verified successful.

Next: Phase 2 - Update CheatManager to respect category toggles
